This commit renames `shutter` to `shutter-encoder` to avoid confusion
with a screenshot application that is also named `shutter`.

* Removed unneeded quotation marks in programs/x86_64/shutter-encoder

* Renamed `shutter` to `shutter-encoder` in programs/x86_64-apps

* Changed how the shutter-encoder script works

Now it should get the actual latest version.
